                            <comment id="13283188" author="brahmareddy" created="Fri, 25 May 2012 07:17:15 +0000"  >
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; newLocalDirs = conf.get(contextCfgItemName);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (!newLocalDirs.equals(savedLocalDirs)) {
				&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; minDiskFreeThresholdMb = conf.getInt(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hadoop.min.local.disk.freespace.threshold&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, 1024);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here newLocalDirs will become null and it&apos;ll throw NPE..&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I did fix like this..&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; newLocalDirs = conf.get(contextCfgItemName);
			&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; == newLocalDirs) {
				&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; IOException(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;dfs.client.buffer.dir not configured&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
			}
      &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (!newLocalDirs.equals(savedLocalDirs) ) {
        localDirs = StringUtils.getTrimmedStrings(newLocalDirs);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
